                <h2 class="title">Implantable Contact Lens (ICL) surgery – A Safe, 
                    Personalized option</h2>
                <p class="paragraph">Lens implantation surgery is a safe alternative for individuals who do not meet the criteria for LASIK surgery. <br/>
                    At Shinsegae Eye Clinic, we perform an in-depth analysis of each patient’s eye condition using over 50 diagnostic tools. Based on the results, we recommend the best, fully customized treatment option.</p>
